{'title':'c1', 'content':[{'slide':'c1s17_11','text':"4. If non-compliance of provision of Chapter 6B of the Act has been found. Then For first time, impose a fine of Nepali Rupees 2 million. For second time, impose a fine of Nepali Rupees 5 million. From third time onwards, impose a fine of Nepali Rupees 20 million or up toRupees50 million as per severity. If there are frequent systemic problems, take action of partial or complete suspension or cancellation of the license."}]},

